<h1>3. muxdev 当前代码实现：不是愿景，而是本地控制面雏形</h1>
<table>
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th background-color="light-gray">能力域</th>
      <th background-color="light-gray">本地代码证据</th>
      <th background-color="light-gray">实现要点</th>
      <th background-color="light-gray">对应痛点</th>
    </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr>
      <td>统一入口</td>
      <td><code>src/muxdev/cli/main.py</code>、<code>src/muxdev/api/</code>、<code>src/muxdev/ui/</code></td>
      <td>CLI、daemon TUI、FastAPI、Dashboard 统一提交与观察任务</td>
      <td>碎片化</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>工作流编排</td>
      <td><code>src/muxdev/runtime/supervisor.py</code>、<code>src/muxdev/workflows/engine.py</code></td>
      <td>创建 run、隔离 worktree、按 DAG 执行 stage、记录 trace 和 artifacts</td>
      <td>碎片化、信任缺失</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>LangGraph 语义桥接</td>
      <td><code>src/muxdev/runtime/langgraph_engine.py</code>、<code>src/muxdev/services/orchestration.py</code></td>
      <td><code>workflow_to_langgraph</code> 可导出 graph spec；执行仍回到 muxdev 审计路径</td>
      <td>碎片化</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>Provider 路由</td>
      <td><code>src/muxdev/providers/adapters.py</code>、<code>src/muxdev/providers/planner.py</code></td>
      <td>Codex、Claude、Qwen、mock 等作为可替换 role backend</td>
      <td>碎片化</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>Provider Action</td>
      <td><code>src/muxdev/storage/blackboard.py</code>、<code>src/muxdev/runtime/stage_attempt.py</code></td>
      <td>把外部 CLI 登录、确认、限流、卡住状态独立记录，不伪装成审批</td>
      <td>治理空白</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>可信交付</td>
      <td><code>src/muxdev/services/evidence.py</code>、<code>src/muxdev/storage/ledger.py</code></td>
      <td>Evidence v2 事件流、manifest、evaluation、hash chain、artifact hash</td>
      <td>信任缺失</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>交付门禁</td>
      <td><code>src/muxdev/services/delivery_gate.py</code></td>
      <td>本地确定性检查 artifact、测试失败、review blocker、runtime error、pending action</td>
      <td>信任缺失、治理空白</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>本地记忆治理</td>
      <td><code>src/muxdev/storage/memory.py</code></td>
      <td>session/run/branch/project/workspace/user 分层，支持证据、审批、矛盾检测和 quarantine</td>
      <td>治理空白</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>恢复与回滚</td>
      <td><code>src/muxdev/runtime/worktree.py</code>、<code>src/muxdev/services/session_capsules.py</code></td>
      <td>隔离 worktree、stage snapshot、handoff patch、session capsule</td>
      <td>信任缺失、治理空白</td>
    </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

